            "text": " out there on the automotive Market that can only be described as small  economic balls of Fun. For example you might think of the beetle, Miata, or an early model Porsche with their small frame and extremely low weight. It also helps that they have styling unlike any other type of vehicle with an emphasis on personality, something many cars lack. One particularly great example of this is the ",
