          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " which you might describe as the brand's flagship economy cruiser. Featured in movies and TV shows Across the globe as the favorite automobile of nerdy teens everywhere, the gremlin fits this description perfectly. So you might see why someone would consider buying one of these vehicles, especially as a ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
